== 0.2.0 / 2009-01-06

Enhancements: 
	* More modular
	* More languages supported
	* Can be installed directly via gem
	* Support config file
	* Width can be specified
	* Space is better used
	* Can be used inside an other program
	* Add tests

Fixes:
	* Die correctly when hit ^C
	* Add separator at the good point
